A new episode of ANOKHI UNCENSORED is out TODAY!!
!
Our Editor-in-Chief HINA P. ANSARI (@hinapansari) had the opportunity to interview a wonderful guest this week . ..

We have the President and Founder of Women Empowerment Awards, (@womenempowermentawards) KLAUDIA ZINATY (@klaudiasfashionfix) 🙌🏼

Here's a glimpse of what they talked about ...

✨ Toronto’s largest event celebrating women entrepreneurs happening on September the 22nd in Toronto, Canada! 💪🏻🇨🇦

✨ How this amazing event came to be and the challenges it faced while it was in the works 

✨ The life lessons Klaudia learned throughout her whole experience with Women Empowerment Awards 🏆 

ALL THIS PLUS MORE!! 🎉

Tune in at Rukusavenueradio.com (@rukusavenueradio) on the Dash Radio (@dashradio) app:
- Tuesday September 18th at 6pm PST/9pm EST
- Wednesday September 19th at 2pm GMT/6.30pm IST

Share this with everyone you feel needs to listen, because trust us, you don't want to miss this one! 💯

Thank you my beautiful Joanne @tinglooks for capturing this moment of pure joy with @irisknowsbest as I watched my incredibly courageous friend @jamstfl walk down the runway for the @arthritissociety.  I’m so PROUD of you for overcoming your daily struggles and bringing awareness to the affect that arthritis has on so many. 

Thank you @daviddixoninc for the invitation in seeing your absolutely stunning accessible collection for those living with arthritis. 

Don’t miss the gala on November 4th to support such an important cause! 🙌🏼

Words cannot describe how proud I am of you @jamstfl and your courage to speak out on living with arthritis. You are one of the kindest, strongest, most determined women I know.  Even when you’re not feeling you’re best, you always put others first and your positive mindset keeps you going. I am so blessed to have you in my life and beyond proud of you!! Please go support her incredible shop @twinfishlux with her unique collection of jewelry and luxe accessories! 🙌🏼❤️

A beautiful night gathered in an intimate setting for a wonderful cause of the Breast Cancer Support fund which bridges the gap between the financial reality faced by breast cancer patients and the limited financial assistance available.

The funds they raise directly support breast cancer patients with meal support programs and financial aid.  Thank you @roger_lamoureux @glenndixon50 @daviddixoninc for having me there, it was a truly special night.

What a wonderful way to end the year! We are thrilled to announce that our latest feature article, highlighting the impactful work of our Women Empowerment Awards, has been published in NY Weekly! Thank you @rhondaswan for your efforts as NY Weekly joins an illustrious list of publications and media outlets that have recognized our commitment to empowering women, including the Toronto Star, Globe and Mail, Living Luxe, Anokhi Media, Yahoo News, and the upcoming issue of Spencer Magazine. Your commitment has not only elevated our visibility but has contributed significantly to the impact we are making in the lives of women entrepreneurs and career professionals. Enthralled to be in conversation with @klaudiasfashionfix Klaudia Zinaty on The Tenzin Show! 

Klaudia is an established Entrepreneur, Media Mogul and Fashion Expert. She is the President and Founder of @womenempowermentawards Women Empowerment Awards. She is also the Former Regional Director of Fashion Group International Toronto. 

To learn more about Klaudia and her success journey, please don’t forget to tune into our episode on January 15th. 

You don’t want to miss this, because her journey is both intriguing and inspiring! If you aspire to be an entrepreneur or want to thrive in your career, I highly recommend that you tune into this episode.
